title: Pica Tinny STL Fusion 360: Pica What ? (Guide of how to create one fast)
description:
Apparently Pica Tinny is hightly printable and usable. So here is how you can create quickly one (or just download my project for stl). And some example of how it works  if you are not use of this pattern.
Source of the project: 
https://github.com/EloiStree3D/2022_06_16_PicaTinnySTL
If you just need the sketch:
https://github.com/EloiStree3D/2022_06_16_PicaTinnySTL/blob/main/Sketch/PicaMeasure2D.dxf

Hope it helps you.
